u=x+vt
\frac{\partial f}{\partial x} = \frac{\partial f}{\partial u}\frac{\partial u}{\partial x} = \frac{\partial f/\partial t}{\partial u/\partial t}\frac{\partial u}{\partial x}=\frac{1}{v}\frac{\partial f}{\partial t}
 \frac{1}{v}\frac{\partial f}{\partial t} =  f
f
f'(x) = f(x)
f
f(x)=A\exp(x)
